  "riddle": "1. Seek the credit card giant established in 1966, whose name resonates globally and influences modern commerce. What year marks its beginning?\n\n2. A famous fast-food chain serves its coffee in a branded café — how many subcategories does the article list under its types and subsidiaries?\n\n3. Located on the Hudson, what city boasts a significant number of libraries close to coordinates 40.71000?\n\n4. Within the heart of a fashion capital, how many residents call this metropolis home, as noted in a prominent report?\n\n5. Ascend to discover how high this city's ground is above sea level, measured in meters.\n\n6. Count the number of libraries surrounding the very same city; how many can you find?\n\n7. From your findings in clues 5 and 6, tally the elevation and library count together.\n\n8. Look back to the urban center previously explored; verify how high its ground rises once more.\n\n9. Now, determine the number of different factors this city's population holds.\n\n10. In a bustling Asian metropolis, what year heralded its establishment, as recorded within the context of its history?\n\n11. Check how elevated this vibrant city stands above sea level. What is the meter count?\n\n12. Count the green spaces nearby; how many parks flourish in the vicinity of this urban titan?\n\n13. Take the absolute difference between your findings from clues 11 and 12 to reveal a number representative of this city's proximity to nature.\n\n14. Within the realms of animation, what year signifies the start of a famed entertainment company’s history, mentioned in the very first segment?\n\n15. Reflect upon that pivotal year; sum the digits together.\n\n16. A state known for its diverse landscapes — how elevated is its terrain, as documented in an informative outline?\n\n17. Finally, calculate the absolute difference between the year from clue 1 and your library count from clue 6, modulo 10. Your answer shall be a single digit representing a unique aspect of the journey through the payments ecosystem.",
